original_title: Jeanine (ou mes parents n'ont rien d'exceptionnel)
overview: Jeanine, ten, can't take it anymore from her parents, former hippies, who only think of having fun. In order to gain access to the square and organized life of which she dreams, she secretly registers for a gymnastics competition with the hope of winning the first prize: a place in a sport studies boarding school.
title: Jeanine (ou mes parents n'ont rien d'exceptionnel)
